Package cz.mff.resler.java.issue_tracking_system

package cz.mff.resler.java.issue_tracking_system
This package contains source classes for the application.

The classes are named after their respective component in the model-view-controller design pattern.

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    App
    The starter class of the application.
    CreateAccountController
    Class for handling the creation of a new account.
    CreateIssueController
    Class that handles the creation of a new issue.
    DashboardController
    Class that handles the dashboard/overview functionality
    DetailIssueController
    Class that handles the issue detail scene
    EditIssueController
    Class that handles the issue editing scene
    Issue
    Class representing an issue in the application.
    IssueModel
    Class for communicating with the database, handling issues.
    LoginController
    Class for handling login input.
    SQLiteConnection
    Class for connecting to the database.
    UserModel
    Class for communicating with the database, handling users.
